   <text type="card">
      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00032.jpeg"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich
                     Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb338" type="place">I. Wollzeile 15</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00033.jpeg"/>L. R.</salute></opener><p>Bitte Nachricht, ob Sie morgen <date>Samſtag</date> mit mir <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KLMAM20191017-10"/>ins Theater<note type="commentary" xml:id="KLMAM20191017-10h"><rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs> ging
                  stattdessen in die Inszenierung der Operette <rs ref="#pmb42293" type="work">Olympia</rs>.</note> wollen (zu »<hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb42289" type="work">Chansonette</rs></hi>«) u ob Sie aufn <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KLMAM21091017-8"/>Gſchnas<note type="commentary" xml:id="KLMAM21091017-8h">(wiener.) Kostümfest.</note> gehn?</p><closer>Herzlich grüßt <signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><p>Bin heute Abend nach <time>10</time> beſti<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>t <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34" type="place">Grst</rs></hi></p></postscript></div></body>
